 font-size:11pt">to engage with customers on their energy usage</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">. It will also help </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">empower customers to amend their energy consumption to reduce their costs and carbon </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">footprint</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt"> by reducing and/or shifting their load. It is therefore important to ensure that the low carbon</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt"> innovation funding is set up to help ensure that these opportunities are realised.</span></li></ol><p style="line-height:12pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 18pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><ol start="26" type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; line-height:12pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 35.45pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">Innovation funding areas that</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt"> the</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt"> Government may wish</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt"> to consider are:</span></li></ol><p style="line-height:12pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><ol type="a" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><ol type="a" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; line-height:12pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 68.17pt; padding-left:3.83pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; font-style:italic">How </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; font-style:italic">the </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; font-style:italic">UK</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; font-style:italic"> realises the end</span><span style="font-family:A